<node id="Structured Grounding">
  <data key="d0">Structured Grounding</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Structured Grounding is a method that helps reduce hallucination in AI outputs by providing a clear foundation based on credible sources and relationships.&lt;SEP&gt;Structured grounding employs knowledge graphs to ensure that model outputs align with verified entities and relationships.</data>
