<node id="EU AI Act">
  <data key="d0">EU AI Act</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The EU AI Act outlines regulatory requirements for artificial intelligence systems, including those used in healthcare.&lt;SEP&gt;The EU AI Act mandates that high-risk AI systems provide adequate traceability and documentation for compliance.&lt;SEP&gt;The EU AI Act establishes the world's first comprehensive regulatory framework for artificial intelligence, entering into force in August 2024.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6f15d160ead15b98ce0ab2ffb63b362a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-13937f8efa1e649021b2562c5c4ce466&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf191c61f24f06aa1b4b87fbbe8f257b</data>
