  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Electronic Health Records are digital versions of patients' paper charts and provide real-world evidence for healthcare knowledge graphs.&lt;SEP&gt;Electronic health records contain patient health information and provide complementary data for vaccine safety monitoring.</data>
