<node id="Graph Neural Networks">
  <data key="d0">Graph Neural Networks</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Graph neural networks are used for automated signal detection in vaccine pharmacovigilance.&lt;SEP&gt;Graph Neural Networks are neural network architectures designed specifically to work with graph data structures for learning representations.</data>
