  <data key="d0">Temporal Knowledge Graphs</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Temporal knowledge graphs capture the evolution of safety evidence over time, facilitating ongoing analysis of vaccine safety.&lt;SEP&gt;Temporal Knowledge Graphs maintain historical states of entities and relationships over time for dynamic querying.</data>
