<node id="Knowledge Graph">
  <data key="d0">Knowledge Graph</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">A Knowledge Graph is a structured representation of entities and their relationships, used for information retrieval and reasoning.&lt;SEP&gt;A Knowledge Graph is a structured representation of knowledge that helps constrain AI model outputs to verified entities and relationships.&lt;SEP&gt;The Knowledge Graph is a structured representation of entities and their relationships, used in Graph RAG for extracting relevant information.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dcf301088ebc124f69bef8c917d94389&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-05b5cd1a96253bf7b78dbf8d300adadd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-884ce470afe0321907650814428fae37</data>
