  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">GraphRAG Systems are systems that use entity and relationship extraction pipelines to build knowledge graphs from raw text.&lt;SEP&gt;GraphRAG Systems are hybrid retrieval systems that utilize reasoning depth, coverage, and traceability in their evaluation metrics.</data>
